&lt;li&gt;Supports computer system validation efforts for Veeva Vault QMS, BMRAM (laboratory information management), analytical lab instruments (e.g., HPLC, UHPLC, PCR instruments, plate readers etc), ERP System (NetSuite).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform risk assessments to determine validation approach and ensure appropriate testing of system functionality, data integrity, and audit trail review.&lt;/li&gt;
